# My Project

## Obondium 

Obondium is a modern website currently being developed. It combines e-commerce and listings functionality with community features. It allows users to upload listings and post business brands, products, services, properties, real estate, jobs etc. The platform also includes an events page to keep users updated on upcoming events, and a jobs page to help them find job openings in their industry. Additionally, the communities and groups page enables users to connect with like-minded individuals and collaborate on projects support various communities and even become part and parcel of campaign teams eyc.

## Features

- User registration and login functionality
- Listing creation and management with custom fields
- E-commerce functionality with shopping cart and payment integration
- Reviews and ratings system for listings
- Events page with RSVP system and integration with Google Calendar
- Jobs page with search functionality and integration with job board APIs
- Communities and groups page with discussion forum and file sharing
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop devices

## Technologies

My Website is built with modern web technologies, including:

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Bootstrap
- jQuery
- PHP
- MySQL


