# Getting Started

To get started with My Website, you will need to clone this repository and install the necessary dependencies. Here are the steps to get started:

1. Clone this repository to your local machine using `git clone https://github.com/derickbond/My-Website.git`
2. Install the necessary dependencies using `npm install`
3. Start the development server using `npm start`
4. Open your web browser and navigate to `http://localhost:3000` to view the website.

